    "text": "Uncle Angelo :Hello children! How are you?Mithini :Hello uncle! We are fine, thanks. Ishini :Uncle, you seem to have changed.Uncle Angelo :Really? How? Mithini :You don't have your beard anymore. What happened?Uncle Angelo :I decided to shave it off. Ishini, you have changed, too. You now have long, wavy hair. It looks very nice.Ishini :Thank you, uncle, but I like straight hair like Mithini's.Mithini :But, I don't like my hair. I wish I had wavy hair like yours.Uncle Angelo :Why not, Mithini? You have beautiful, straight, black hair. (Mithini picks up a photograph from the coffee table.)Mithini :Who is this gentleman,uncle? Uncle Angelo :He is my new boss, Mr.Ravi Rajan.Mithini :He is very tall and fair in complexion, isn't he?",
