  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      450.28,
      454.05,
      526.44
    ],
    "text": "Nik, a Labrador cross has been missing since 3rd May. Last seen wearing a red collar with a name tag. The license number is D5498. Nik is golden brown in colour and has a black snout. There is a white patch on its head. If found, please contact the closest Police Station or call 1122432432. A handsome reward awaits anyone who provides any information on Nik.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.995999813079834,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      71.98,
      540.09,
      454.04,
      616.44
    ],
    "text": "(2) FoundA brown colour, men's wallet with money and two credit cards in it was found yesterday (10th June) around 4.30 p.m. near the Children\u2019s Park on Park Street, Colombo 05. The owner can contact the security office of the Children\u2019s Park to claim the wallet.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.995999813079834,
      12.0
    ]
  },
