      72.0,
      50.25,
      292.34,
      66.61
    ],
    "text": "(3) Guess who it is...",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      80.45,
      453.05,
      186.61
    ],
    "text": "Attention please! Welcome to \u201cGuess who he is\u201d competition. This competition is open to all. We will read a description of a person who is here at the carnival. All you have to do is to find him and bring him to the registration desk. Our mystery person today is a man. He is about 5 feet and 10 inches tall and is dark-complexioned. He has a big birthmark on his left cheek. He is wearing a white colour, long-sleeved shirt, a pair of black trousers, a white hat and a pair of black sandals. Hurry! Find him and win a prize.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
